        "content": "<p>Zulip can turn PR and issue numbers into GitHub links, but is there a way to set the destination repository per-stream? Right now they all seem to go to <code>rust-lang/rust</code>.</p>",
        "id": 187077764,
        "sender_full_name": "Laurențiu",
        "timestamp": 1580472924
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>It isn't per stream, it's globally configured in Organization Settings &gt; Linkifiers.</p>",
        "id": 187077985,
        "sender_full_name": "davidtwco",
        "timestamp": 1580473186
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Ah, too bad :-(</p>",
