        "sender_full_name": "Laurențiu",
        "timestamp": 1580473203
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><code>org-name/repo-name#XYZ</code> works though, and we can do short versions like <code>repo-name#XYZ</code> for commonly-referred-to repos.</p>",
